[4:36 PM] Patient: Can you explain more?

[4:36 PM] Eve: Hello, and welcome. I'm Eve, your AI assistant trained to support you with psycho-oncology assessments. Regular wellbeing check-ins are an important part of your healing process, and I'm here to help guide you through this. How have you been feeling about your treatment lately?

[4:36 PM] Patient: Not sure

[4:36 PM] Patient: No

[4:36 PM] Eve: Of course. Regular wellbeing assessments help us understand how you're coping with your cancer treatment, both emotionally and mentally. We focus on areas like anxiety, depression, distress, self-efficacy, and support systems. This helps us provide recommendations to enhance your overall wellbeing. It's okay if you're not sure about your feelings; we can explore them together. Shall we start with how you've been feeling about your treatment recently?
